41:51.117 --> 41:54.250
Rise and shine, Papa.

41:54.294 --> 41:56.296
The clouds are gone.

41:56.339 --> 41:58.994
It's a glorious day, Papa.

42:01.170 --> 42:02.824
Papa?

42:05.435 --> 42:07.350
Papa!

42:07.394 --> 42:08.917
[gasps]

42:15.315 --> 42:17.360
[knock on door]

42:25.847 --> 42:27.370
We have to talk.

42:28.546 --> 42:30.373
Yeah. Yeah, I'd like to talk.

42:30.417 --> 42:32.375
I'm ashamed
of how I left things.

42:32.419 --> 42:33.594
Now, just forget about it.

42:33.638 --> 42:35.509
No, I have to explain.

42:35.553 --> 42:37.032
The truth is, I...

42:37.076 --> 42:38.860
I'm in so much trouble.

42:38.904 --> 42:40.862
And lately it's felt like

42:40.906 --> 42:42.647
you're my best friend
in the world.

42:42.690 --> 42:44.387
So, I'm back.

42:44.431 --> 42:46.868
Because I trust you
to give me good advice.

42:46.912 --> 42:49.044
See, the...

42:49.088 --> 42:50.829
The thing
I couldn't tell you was...

42:50.872 --> 42:52.352
You're pregnant.

42:54.397 --> 42:55.442
How?

42:55.485 --> 42:57.183
I am a detective.

42:57.226 --> 42:59.315
Oh, Vern.

43:00.839 --> 43:02.362
What am I gonna do?

43:02.405 --> 43:04.625
Here's a thought.

43:04.669 --> 43:06.453
Marry me.

43:06.496 --> 43:08.237
What?

43:09.978 --> 43:12.502
Look, if you're just trying
to be a good guy here...

43:12.546 --> 43:14.722
No. That's not what this is.

43:16.202 --> 43:18.639
But you'd be raising
another man's baby.

43:18.683 --> 43:21.294
With the woman I love.

43:21.337 --> 43:22.948
[gasps]

43:22.991 --> 43:25.211
Oh, Vern.

43:25.254 --> 43:26.778
Are you absolutely sure?

43:26.821 --> 43:28.518
Oh, yeah.

43:28.562 --> 43:30.390
I've given it a lot of thought.

43:30.433 --> 43:31.783
In fact...

43:32.784 --> 43:35.047
I bought this for you
last night.

43:36.439 --> 43:38.093
I hope it's okay.

43:39.051 --> 43:40.618
[gasps]

43:45.971 --> 43:48.451
Sorry for being so blunt.

43:48.495 --> 43:50.236
I probably should have had
a fancy speech prepared.

43:50.279 --> 43:51.541
But...

43:53.282 --> 43:54.457
But if you'll have me...

43:54.501 --> 43:56.546
[crying]

44:03.684 --> 44:05.381
I guess that's a yes, huh?

44:05.425 --> 44:07.819
Oh. That's more than a yes.

44:07.862 --> 44:09.821
That's a "you betcha."

44:09.864 --> 44:11.823
[both laughing]

44:19.700 --> 44:21.702
[snoring]

44:31.364 --> 44:33.409
[snoring continues]

44:39.764 --> 44:40.808
