45:07.269 --> 45:08.706
Hello.

45:08.749 --> 45:09.968
Yes, hello.

45:10.011 --> 45:12.622
My name is Mary Booth.

45:12.666 --> 45:14.363
I live in your neighborhood.

45:14.407 --> 45:17.105
I drove by your home
and saw the ambulance.

45:17.149 --> 45:18.672
I was concerned.

45:18.716 --> 45:21.283
Did something happen
to Mr. Castillo?

45:21.327 --> 45:22.894
Yes.

45:22.937 --> 45:24.547
My father died last night.

45:24.591 --> 45:26.071
Oh, no.

45:26.114 --> 45:27.855
Well, um...

45:27.899 --> 45:30.466
This is just awful of me to ask,

45:30.510 --> 45:32.642
but do you know how he died?

45:32.686 --> 45:34.209
What do you mean?

45:34.253 --> 45:36.995
Well, I was in a cafÃ© last week,

45:37.038 --> 45:39.084
and I overheard his wife Rita

45:39.127 --> 45:41.477
saying the most awful things
about him

45:41.521 --> 45:43.523
and the money
that she expected to inherit.

45:43.566 --> 45:47.005
Uh, "Any day now"
was the phrase that she used.

45:47.048 --> 45:49.007
When you said that he'd died,

45:49.050 --> 45:52.010
the hairs on the back of my neck
just stood up.

45:52.053 --> 45:54.447
I...

45:54.490 --> 45:56.492
Maybe it's wrong of me,
but I felt that I had

45:56.536 --> 45:57.755
